  "texts": [
    "See Table 7 for theme descriptions and \"Appendix 4\" for included articles and associated themes.",
    "Continuous monitoring and adjustment were identified as a measure to ensure accuracy and safety in the rapidly changing and unpredictable settings where AI-enabled systems were used [36,38].",
    "Various methods were highlighted, including:• Tracking trends and detecting anomalies [8].• Conducting retroactive pilots before deploying new versions [8].",
    "• Continuously calibrating and adjusting the AI-enabled systems to adapt to changes in the physical environment [14].",
    "• Monitoring and evaluating user feedback to prevent skewed outputs resulting from inadequate user feedback [6].Collecting real-world data The included literature emphasised the importance of high-quality, high-integrity data for training AI-enabled systems to prevent harm and foster stakeholder trust [39,40]."
  ]
